com.tedros.fxapi.annotation.reader

Annotation Type TByteArrayReader


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface TByteArrayReader
     Build a TByteArrayReader
 which is a StackPane with a ImageView and a open button. 

 Types supported:
 
 SimpleObjectProperty<byte[]>
    Author:
    Davis Gordon
